Class PojoPropertyAccessorProxySetByKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.pojo.descriptor.base.accessor.AbstractPojoPropertyAccessor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PojoPropertyAccessor, PojoPropertyAccessorOneArg, PojoAttributeName

    public class PojoPropertyAccessorProxySetByKey
extends AbstractPojoPropertyAccessorProxy
implements PojoPropertyAccessorOneArg
    This is an implementation of the PojoPropertyAccessorOneArg acting as as a setter that delegates to a mapped-setter using a fixed key.
    Since:
    1.1.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
